ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND v. OWENS HAYNES [Misc. (BV) No. 27,

September Term, 1982.]

Order filed December 28, 1982.

Consent to disbarment filed by Owens Haynes in accordance with Maryland Rule BV12 d 2.

Owens Haynes is disbarred by consent from the further practice of law in the State of Maryland and his name stricken from the register of attorneys in this Court.
